caption: A statue of Buddha with intricate carvings.
distinguishing_feature: Buddhist iconography: Buddha/monk with ushnisha or shaved head, elongated earlobes/urna, serene expression, and meditative or prayer poses (e.g., lotus, dhyana, anjali).
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict Buddhist figures (Buddha or Buddhist monk) with characteristic features and poses. Group_b shows assorted non-Buddhist statues (historical figures, athletes, animals, etc.).
query_details: Colorful temple facade with three ornate standing deities wearing crowns and jewelry—Hindu iconography, not Buddha/monk; no ushnisha/lotus meditation pose.

caption: A bunch of vibrant flowers.
distinguishing_feature: A close-up bouquet/cluster of cut flowers without any container or broad environmental scene.
analysis: Group_a images are tight close-ups of cut flowers/bouquets or clustered flower heads with no pot/vase or broad scene visible. Group_b images show flowers in wider contexts (gardens, storefront, landscapes) or in containers (pots/vases), plus an unrelated item.
query_details: A wide outdoor landscape of a sunflower field stretching to the horizon—clearly a broad scene, not a bouquet.

caption: A fox playing in the snow.
distinguishing_feature: A fox present in a snowy landscape (fox + snow together).
analysis: Group_a always shows a fox in a snowy environment. Group_b either has snow without a fox (snowman, skier, car, birds) or a fox not in snow (grass/forest).
query_details: A dark-coated fox running through deep snow.

caption: A close-up view of pink tulips.
distinguishing_feature: Tulip blossoms: smooth, upright green stems with cup-shaped petals characteristic of tulips.
analysis: All group_a images depict tulip flowers (cup-shaped blooms on smooth, upright stems), while group_b mostly shows other flower types (iris, daisy, orchid, poppy, roses) with one exception of yellow tulips. Thus, the consistent cue is the presence of tulips.
query_details: Shows a bed of white tulips with classic cup-shaped blooms and tall smooth stems.

caption: Lightning hitting through cloudy sky.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of bright, jagged lightning bolts/electrical discharges in the sky.
analysis: All group_a images show visible lightning bolts in stormy skies. Group_b images depict skies, clouds, sunsets, or other scenes without any lightning.
query_details: City skyline under storm clouds with multiple jagged lightning bolts across the sky.

caption: Golden Gate Bridge.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of the Golden Gate Bridge: red/orange suspension design with tall twin towers and vertical cables.
analysis: Group_a consistently shows the Golden Gate Bridge—large red/orange suspension bridge with tall towers and cables—captured from different angles or as a painting. Group_b shows other types of gates or small generic bridges (wooden footbridges, garden gates, castle gate) without the Golden Gate’s distinctive red towers and suspension cables.
query_details: A small arched wooden footbridge over a stream in a lush garden; no red towers or suspension cables.

caption: A seal lounging in the penguin colony.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of both a pinniped (seal/sea lion/elephant seal) and penguins together on land/shore.
analysis: All group_a images show seals/sea lions/elephant seals together with standing penguins on shore or beach. Group_b images lack this specific on-land coexistence; they show lone animals, underwater scenes, or predators, but not seals among standing penguins on land.
query_details: An elephant seal in shallow water at the shoreline with many standing king penguins behind it on the beach.

caption: Flags floating on a flagpole.
distinguishing_feature: Flag displayed on a tall, fixed outdoor flagpole (ground-mounted mast) reaching into the sky.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show flags flown on tall, fixed outdoor flagpoles (ground-mounted masts) against open sky. Group_b images show flags in other contexts: handheld, wall-mounted, tabletop, close-up fabric, or illustrations—not on tall, fixed flagpoles.
query_details: A U.S. flag mounted on a short angled pole attached to a house—not a tall, ground-mounted flagpole.

caption: A ladybug on a green leaf.
distinguishing_feature: A red/orange, black-spotted ladybug (Coccinellidae) positioned on green leaves/grass.
analysis: All group_a images depict the classic red/orange, black-spotted ladybird beetle on green foliage. Group_b includes other insects or ladybirds in non-leaf settings (stone, ground, spider web) or different beetle types/colors.
query_details: Shows three metallic blue-green beetles on a leaf; not red/orange and not the spotted ladybug form.

caption: Lighting candles on a birthday cake.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a cake with lit birthday candles on it.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show birthday cakes with lit candles on top. Group_b shows candles in other contexts (decor, making, melted, dining) or cakes without candles, and even a bulb—no candles on cakes.
query_details: A single lit candle against a dark background with no cake present.

caption: Cabinets in the kitchen room.
distinguishing_feature: Prominent, central presence of kitchen cabinets/storage (doors, drawers, pull-outs) as the primary visual focus.
analysis: Group_a images consistently emphasize kitchen cabinetry/storage as the main subject—multiple cabinet doors, drawers, pull-out organizers, or full cabinet runs dominate the frame. Group_b images focus on other kitchen elements or activities (towels, cooking, sinks, pouring water, bar seating, hardware close-up) rather than the cabinetry itself.
query_details: Shows a cooktop with a stainless range hood flanked by large wooden cabinet doors—cabinetry is a major visual element in the scene.

caption: White smoke against black background.
distinguishing_feature: Neutral grayscale smoke on a solid black background.
analysis: Group_a images show white/gray smoke rendered in neutral grayscale against a solid black background. Group_b images feature colored backgrounds or tinted smoke (yellow, red, pink, purple, orange) and non‑black/bright backgrounds.
query_details: Green background with green-tinted smoke; not grayscale on black.

caption: A bouquet of roses.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of rose flowers as the primary subject.
analysis: All group_a images depict bouquets/arrangements of roses (various colors, but clearly rose blooms). Group_b contains non-rose subjects (food, fruits) and other flowers like lilies and sunflowers.
query_details: A bouquet of orange and purple tulips tied with a ribbon—no rose blooms present.

caption: Pieces of chess.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a chessboard and/or chess pieces.
analysis: All group_a images depict chess sets—boards and/or chess pieces. Group_b images show unrelated items (pottery, toolbox, fruit, toy cars, jigsaw puzzle, building blocks).
query_details: Illustrated chessboard with pieces in the starting position and coordinates.

caption: Chimney on the house roof.
distinguishing_feature: An exterior chimney stack visible on a roof (outdoors) vs. indoor fireplaces or non-chimney scenes.
analysis: Group_a consistently shows exterior rooftop chimney stacks on houses, often against the sky. Group_b contains indoor fireplaces or unrelated subjects and does not show exterior chimneys.
query_details: An indoor brick fireplace with burning logs and fireplace tools; no exterior rooftop chimney present.

caption: The lush green rice fields.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of rice paddy structure: leveed/bunded plots (often flooded) with dense thin rice blades uniformly covering the field.
analysis: Group_a images depict rice paddies—flat or terraced plots separated by bunds, often water-filled, with dense, uniform, bright‑green rice shoots. Group_b images are gardens, meadows/pastures, forests, or dry row crops and lack the flooded paddy layout and rice seedlings.
query_details: Shows a farmer with a buffalo plowing water-filled, bunded plots containing young rice seedlings.

caption: A well trimmed bonsai tree in a pot.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a bonsai: a miniature tree with a woody trunk and styled/pruned canopy grown in a shallow bonsai container.
analysis: Group_a images all depict bonsai—miniature trees with woody trunks, trained/pruned canopies, typically in shallow bonsai pots. Group_b shows non-bonsai items: regular potted flowers/herbs/cacti and pottery/teaware; they lack the tree-like, pruned bonsai form.
query_details: A red-leaf miniature tree (maple) with a woody trunk and shaped canopy in a decorative shallow pot, classic bonsai presentation.

caption: Interlocking necklaces.
distinguishing_feature: Interlocking/complimentary parts that fit together or overlap to form a whole (e.g., puzzle pieces, linked hearts) rather than a single standalone charm.
analysis: Group_a necklaces feature components that interlock, overlap, or fit together (puzzle pieces, two halves of a heart, interwoven heart and infinity, linked hearts), often as matching sets. Group_b pieces are standalone pendants or charms (letters, bird, simple heart, non-interlaced infinity).
query_details: A single round pendant with a tree-of-life cutout—one standalone charm with no interlocking or paired elements.

caption: Doctors operate on patients.
distinguishing_feature: Active surgery in a sterile operating room environment (surgeons in masks/caps/gloves with surgical tools/microscopes and OR lights).
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict active surgical procedures in an operating room: surgeons in full sterile attire, operating microscopes/lights, and surgical instruments. Group_b images show non-surgical settings such as wards, recovery, waiting areas, or diagrams.
query_details: A patient lying in a hospital bed with a nurse in a recovery/ward setting; text says 'Post-Op Healing'; no surgical tools or OR lights; not an operation in progress.

caption: An old barn in the lush grassy fields.
distinguishing_feature: A real photograph of a visibly aged/dilapidated farm building (barn/shed) with rust, peeling paint, or structural wear.
analysis: All group_a images show old, weathered farm buildings (barns/sheds) with clear signs of age or disrepair—rusted roofs, peeling paint, warped boards, sagging or missing panels. Group_b images either feature non-barn subjects (machinery, ramp), a modern well-kept house, a distant generic house, or even a painted barn (artwork), not a clearly dilapidated real barn.
query_details: Shows a rustic barn with faded/peeling blue siding and worn open doors, surrounded by overgrown flowers/grass—looks aged and weathered.

caption: Ball bats.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a bat (long solid club) used to hit a ball, as in baseball/cricket—not hands, feet, or rackets.
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict bat-and-ball sports (baseball/cricket) with an elongated bat striking or being held near a ball. Group_b images involve balls without bats (football, juggling, handball, toys).
query_details: Shows a tennis racket contacting a tennis ball; a strung racket is present, not a bat.

caption: A wooden floor in the living room.
distinguishing_feature: Residential/home interior versus commercial/public or professional space.
analysis: Group_a images depict cozy residential/home-style interiors (living rooms, stairs, seating corners) with soft furnishings and decor; group_b shows commercial/public spaces (coffee shop, restaurants, studios, dance studio) with industrial fixtures like black metal chairs, signage, mirrors, or recording equipment.
query_details: Bright living room with sofa, armchairs, rug, fireplace, wood floor, and houseplant—clearly a home interior.

caption: Chocolate chip cookies.
distinguishing_feature: Visible chocolate chips or chunks embedded on the cookie surface.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show chocolate chip cookies with visible chocolate chips/chunks on the surface (including in stacks and ice cream sandwiches). Group_b shows other treats or cookies without visible chocolate chips (icing, sprinkles, crinkle sugar, crosshatch patterns, etc.).
query_details: Light-colored cookies with smooth tops and a few almond slices; no visible chocolate chips or chunks.

caption: A painting of a woman with a distorted head.
distinguishing_feature: Stylized abstract portraiture (cubist/surreal/graphic treatment with unnatural colors and simplified shapes) versus realistic or photographic depiction.
analysis: Group_a images are stylized/abstract portraits with exaggerated shapes, bold or unnatural color blocks, and surreal or geometric elements. Group_b images are photographs or realistic/representational paintings with natural proportions and shading.
query_details: A realistic digital painting of a woman in profile with a translucent veil, natural proportions and soft lighting; not abstract or geometrically stylized.

caption: Colorful ribbons.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of multicolored/rainbow ribbons or multiple differently colored ribbons together (vs. single-color ribbons).
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature ribbons/streamers that are visibly multicolored (rainbow or multiple different ribbon colors shown together). Group_b images show ribbons that are typically single-colored (red, white, gold) or the multicolor elements are not on ribbons.
query_details: A pile of curled ribbon that is entirely red—single color.

caption: A variety of sweet drinks.
distinguishing_feature: Beverage presented in clear, transparent glassware with visible contents.
analysis: All group_a images show beverages served in transparent glassware where the drink itself is clearly visible (pitchers, jars, flutes, tumblers), often colorful/iced. Group_b includes mixed containers—opaque mugs, bottles, and some glasses—so the drink is not consistently visible.
query_details: A canned sparkling water in an opaque aluminum can; the beverage itself is not visible.

caption: Yellow daffodils.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a daffodil flower with six petals and a central trumpet-shaped corona.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show yellow daffodils: six flat petals around a prominent central trumpet (corona), often with long narrow leaves. Group_b contains other yellow subjects (roses, poppies/paintings, objects, animals, etc.) and no daffodil structure.
query_details: A yellow daisy-like flower with many slender petals and no central trumpet.

caption: Bamboo baskets.
distinguishing_feature: Natural plant-fiber weaving (wicker/rattan/bamboo) as the primary material and texture.
analysis: Group_a images all show baskets woven from natural plant fibers (wicker/rattan/bamboo) with an interlaced organic texture. Group_b shows baskets/containers made from other materials: metal mesh, plastic, paper origami, or wooden slats.
query_details: A brown basket with an interlaced weave and a woven handle made of natural-looking fibers.

caption: A perched mantis hanging on a plant.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a praying mantis with folded raptorial forelegs and triangular head.
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict a praying mantis on vegetation, identifiable by its triangular head and folded raptorial forelegs. Group_b mostly shows other subjects (butterfly decor, caterpillar, bird, ladybug, bee) with only one image featuring a mantis.
query_details: Close-up of a praying mantis with long antennae and folded raptorial forelegs.

caption: A bunch of flowers with yellow stamens.
distinguishing_feature: Flowers photographed growing on the plant (not cut or arranged in a bouquet or artificial composition).
analysis: Group_a images show live flowers in situ—blooms attached to plants with natural foliage/backgrounds. Group_b images are man‑made compositions: bouquets in vases, still-life setups, or artificial/arranged bunches.
query_details: A single lavender flower attached to its stem amid green leaves outdoors—clearly a live plant, not an arrangement.

caption: City bridge over the river at night.
distinguishing_feature: Nighttime/low-light bridge scenes with visible artificial lighting (streetlights, city lights, illuminated structures).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show bridges at night or in low light with artificial lights on (often reflecting on water). Group_b images are in daylight/sunrise with natural light and no active night lighting.
query_details: Dark, low-light scene with bridges and numerous lights illuminated along the spans; snowy riverside walkway.

caption: An aerial view of the city.
distinguishing_feature: Primary subject is a dense urban skyline/cityscape with prominent high-rise buildings or iconic city landmarks (urban dominance) versus nature/rural-dominated scenes.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show dense urban cityscapes/skyline views (often from an elevated or aerial perspective) featuring iconic metropolitan landmarks and many high-rise buildings. Group_b images are mostly natural or rural scenes (farms, rivers, deserts, mountains, patchwork fields); the one city view includes a strong natural foreground and is not primarily a skyline focus.
query_details: An elevated view of a large coastal city with dense buildings and a prominent landmark statue overlooking a bay—clearly an urban skyline/cityscape.

caption: A seagull walking on the beach.
distinguishing_feature: A seagull on the ground at the beach/shoreline (visible legs, not flying or perched).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show seagulls standing or walking on the ground at the beach/shoreline (sand, rocks, or shallow water). Group_b includes other animals and seagulls that are flying, perched on branches, or otherwise not standing on the beach.
query_details: A seagull standing on sandy beach near the waterline, legs visible, not flying or perched.

caption: Propeller aircraft.
distinguishing_feature: Fixed-wing aircraft with visible propellers.
analysis: Group_a images all depict fixed‑wing airplanes powered by propellers (including seaplanes and vintage biplanes). Group_b consists of aircraft without that combo: jets, helicopters/multirotors, and a blimp—no fixed‑wing prop planes.
query_details: An airliner over the ocean at sunset with jet engines under the wings and no propellers.

caption: A variety of colorful lollipops.
distinguishing_feature: Candy attached to a stick (lollipop).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show lollipops—candy mounted on a stick. Group_b shows assorted candies without sticks (bar, gummies, mints, truffles, bagged hard candy), with an occasional exception (candied apple on a stick).
query_details: A glass bowl filled with multicolored round gumballs; no sticks present.

caption: Snow mountain ridge.
distinguishing_feature: Dominant presence of snow creating a wintry landscape (snow-covered surfaces and active snowfall).
analysis: All group_a images show winter scenes with snow-covered ground/trees/mountains and activities in snowy conditions. Most group_b images feature non-winter landscapes (greenery, wildlife, water) with little to no snow; one exception shows snow-clearing machinery, but snow is not consistent across group_b.
query_details: A landscape blanketed in snow with heavy snowfall and snow-covered trees.

caption: Military helicopters are carrying out rescues.
distinguishing_feature: Active rescue/medevac operation with an external hoist/long-line (often with personnel or loads) and emergency/relief context.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show helicopters engaged in rescue/medevac or military relief operations—hoists/long-lines, stretcher carries, emergency symbols, and active extractions. Group_b shows civilian/general-use helicopters in cockpits, on pads, or simple flight without rescue action.
query_details: A helicopter is hoisting a person on a long line between buildings—an active rescue/hoist scene.

caption: Bright red maple leaves in autumn.
distinguishing_feature: Dominant red maple foliage (multiple palmate, lobed leaves or a whole red maple tree) photographed outdoors as the main subject.
analysis: Group_a consistently shows red autumn maple foliage as the dominant subject—clusters of lobed leaves or entire red trees in natural, outdoor scenes. Group_b is mixed: graphics, studio/isolated leaves, non-maple plants (roses), green leaves, or general autumn woods; only a few contain red maple leaves.
query_details: Branches filled with many red, lobed maple leaves backlit by the sun against a blue sky—an outdoor scene where red maple foliage is the focus.

caption: Lighting candles on a birthday cake.
distinguishing_feature: Lit candles positioned on top of a cake.
analysis: All group_a images show lit candles placed on top of a cake (birthday-style). Group_b images feature candles not on cakes or cakes without candles (or candle-like objects).
query_details: A white cake with seven tall gold candles on top, all lit.

caption: Wooden wheels.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of wheels—objects designed to roll (often with wooden wheels).
analysis: Group_a images all depict wheeled vehicles/objects (wagons, carts, a wooden bike, a toy car), typically with prominent wooden wheels. Group_b mostly shows non-wheeled wooden items (chair, table, ladder, windmill) with some trains, so wheels are not consistent there.
query_details: A vintage car with large spoked wheels (wooden spokes), clearly a wheeled vehicle.

caption: A huge cargo ship.
distinguishing_feature: Visible stacks of standardized rectangular shipping containers on deck (container ship).
analysis: group_a images are all container ships with clearly visible stacks of standardized rectangular shipping containers and often container cranes. group_b consists of other vessels (sailboat, wreck, ship under construction, tug/barge, general cargo ship) without visible container stacks.
query_details: A large white cruise ship with many passenger decks and smooth sides, no visible containers or container cranes.

caption: Christmas illustration.
distinguishing_feature: Explicit traditional Christmas decorations/icons presented in a typical festive context (e.g., decorated tree, stockings, wreaths, presents, Santa/gingerbread).
analysis: Group_a consistently shows clear, traditional Christmas iconography in a normal festive setting (decorated trees, stockings, wreaths, presents, Santa/gingerbread, caroling). Group_b either lacks these decorations or places Christmas elements in odd/non-traditional contexts (plain undecorated tree, desert/beach scenes, Halloween mix, generic winter play).
query_details: Cozy indoor scene with a decorated Christmas tree, stockings on the fireplace, wreaths/garlands, and many presents—classic Christmas setting.

caption: A small plush animal toy.
distinguishing_feature: Being a soft, plush, stuffed animal toy (fuzzy fabric formed into an animal with a face and limbs).
analysis: Group_a images are all soft, plush, stuffed animal toys with fuzzy fabric and clear animal shapes/faces. Group_b items are not plush stuffed animals: they are wooden/plastic/rubber toys or a fuzzy blanket (soft but not an animal toy).
query_details: Shows multiple small plush cat figures with fuzzy texture and stuffed, 3D animal shapes and faces.

caption: Interlocking necklaces.
distinguishing_feature: Interlocking or complementary components that fit together or link (e.g., puzzle pieces, linked hearts), often symbolizing a pair/union.
analysis: Group_a pendants consistently feature two or more shapes that interlock or form complementary pieces of a whole (puzzle pieces, lock & key halves, intertwined heart/infinity, linked hearts). Group_b pieces are standalone single charms (letters, bird, single heart/infinity) without interlocking/complementary parts.
query_details: A pendant with two interlocking circles linked together.

caption: Climbers celebrating at the top of a mountain.
distinguishing_feature: Being on the very top/crest of a mountain and posing/celebrating (summit shot) versus being mid‑climb/hike/camp.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show people at the summit or on a prominent peak/crest, often posing or celebrating with a panoramic backdrop. Group_b images show in‑progress activities—indoor wall climbing, hiking, camping, or moving along ridges—rather than a summit pose.
query_details: A climber actively ascending a rocky section with rope and gear; mid-climb, not posed on a summit.

caption: Wedding photos of the bride and groom.
distinguishing_feature: Primary focus on only the bride and groom (no large group), as an intimate couple portrait.
analysis: Group_a images are couple-focused wedding portraits: the bride and groom are the clear, primary subjects, usually alone (no large group) in outdoor settings. Group_b images show groups, preparations, reception activities, or non-couple-focused scenes.
query_details: A large group wedding photo on a beach with many people posing together, not just the couple.

caption: Elderly person using a cell phone.
distinguishing_feature: Person is actively holding/using a mobile phone.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show people using mobile phones (smartphones or feature phones). Group_b shows people using other items/devices (tablet, laptop, book, letters, handheld game console) but not phones.
query_details: The person on the bench is holding and looking at a smartphone.

caption: An orchestra performing a symphony concert.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a classical orchestra/choir setup with many seated musicians, sheet music stands, and typically a conductor in a formal concert hall.
analysis: Group_a images show classical concert settings: large seated ensembles (or choir/orchestra), music stands, acoustic string sections, and a conductor in formal concert halls. Group_b images depict popular/club shows: small bands or DJs with electric instruments, microphones, stage lighting effects, and no conductor.
query_details: A grand concert hall with an orchestra on stage, many seated musicians and music stands, consistent with a symphonic performance.

caption: Doctors debugging reagents in the laboratory.
distinguishing_feature: Hands-on manipulation of laboratory/testing equipment or samples in a lab/cleanroom environment, with no patient present.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show people in lab/cleanroom settings handling laboratory equipment or samples (test tubes, pipettes, petri dishes, microscopes), with PPE and no patients present. Group_b images depict clinical care or healthcare contexts (patients, surgery, staff meetings, promotional/illustrative healthcare content) rather than lab bench work.
query_details: A person in a lab coat and gloves is holding a technical instrument next to a monitor in a sterile-looking room; no patient is visible.

caption: Military carriers.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of military hardware/personnel (armored vehicles, mounted guns, soldiers, or military helicopters).
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict military contexts: armored vehicles, mounted weapons, soldiers in combat gear, and military helicopters. Group_b shows civilian transportation and everyday/emergency road scenes (cars, trucks, trains, commercial airliner).
query_details: A line of civilian cars in traffic; no military equipment or soldiers visible.

caption: A man is training at the gym.
distinguishing_feature: Subject is actively engaged in a workout movement (exercise in progress) rather than resting, idle, or distracted.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show people actively performing an exercise (running, push-ups, cycling, lifting, rowing, pull-ups). Group_b mostly shows non-exercise moments—resting, using a phone, walking with a bag, or sleeping—though one image includes an exercise.
query_details: Person is curling a loaded barbell, clearly in the act of lifting.

caption: A symbol of king.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a crown/royal crown imagery.
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature a crown or explicit royal regalia. Group_b shows medieval/fantasy symbols (castle, horse, jester, dragon, shield) but no crowns.
query_details: A sword with wings topped by a jeweled crown.

caption: Pieces of chess.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of chess elements (chessboard/checkerboard and recognizable chess pieces such as king, queen, rook, knight, bishop, pawns).
analysis: All group_a images depict chess sets—boards and/or chess pieces. None of the group_b images relate to chess; they show unrelated objects (tools, fruit, cars, puzzle, blocks, etc.).
query_details: A boxed silverware set with forks, knives, and spoons; no chessboard or chess pieces.

caption: A bride holding colored flowers.
distinguishing_feature: A bride in a white wedding dress visibly holding a bouquet.
analysis: All group_a images feature a bride in a white wedding dress holding a floral bouquet. Group_b images either lack a bouquet or the person holding flowers is not a bride (e.g., child, groom), or the focus is on other elements.
query_details: A man in a dark suit is holding a large bouquet; no bride or white wedding dress is visible.

caption: Ball bats.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a baseball or cricket bat being held or used to strike a ball.
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict bat-and-ball sports (baseball/cricket) with a clear wooden or plastic bat present. Group_b images show other activities with balls (football, juggling, ball pit, handball) and no baseball/cricket bat.
query_details: A cricket batsman holding a cricket bat near the stumps with a wicketkeeper behind—clearly a bat-and-ball scene.

caption: A well trimmed bonsai tree in a pot.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a bonsai-style miniature tree: a woody trunk with branching shaped like a small tree, typically in a shallow bonsai pot.
analysis: Group_a images all show bonsai or bonsai-styled miniature trees with a woody trunk and trained branching in a shallow pot. Group_b shows other items: general potted plants (herbs, cactus, sunflower) and pottery/tea ware, lacking the bonsai form with a woody trunk.
query_details: A miniature tree with a woody trunk and branched canopy bearing decorative leaves/flowers in a shallow, ornate pot—an ornamental bonsai-like piece.

caption: Snow mountain ridge.

analysis: All group_a images show snowy alpine settings that include a clear human presence or man‑made object (people, cabin, helicopter, climbing gear). query_details: Snowy mountains at sunrise with no people, buildings, or equipment visible.

caption: A man cuts meat on a cutting board.
distinguishing_feature: Hands actively cutting raw red meat with a knife on a cutting board.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show hands actively using a knife/cleaver to cut raw red meat on a cutting board. Group_b images involve cutting fruits/vegetables or handling fish/chicken or meat without the active cutting action.
query_details: Hands are slicing cubes of raw red meat with a knife on a wooden board.

distinguishing_feature: Active bench laboratory activity with lab-specific tools and samples (e.g., test tubes, pipettes, petri dishes, microscopes) in a lab environment, without patient interaction.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show people performing laboratory work—handling samples with gloves and lab tools (test tubes, pipettes, petri dishes, microscopes) in a lab/cleanroom. query_details: Pills being counted on a pharmacy tray into an orange prescription bottle—medication dispensing, not lab experimentation.

distinguishing_feature: A bride visibly holding a bridal bouquet.

caption: A man playing the drum kit.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a standard drum kit (multiple drums and cymbals on stands) being played with drumsticks.
analysis: All group_a images show a person playing a standard drum kit with cymbals and drumsticks. Group_b images show other musical contexts (singers, strings, woodwinds, brass, hand percussion) without a full drum kit.
query_details: A musician playing an electric guitar on stage; no drum kit or cymbals present.

caption: Aerial view of the city centre.

analysis: Group_a images are all measuring instruments with graduated scales/units (thermometer, multimeter, caliper, barometer, scale, measuring tape). Group_b are action tools used to cut, fasten, drill, paint, or strike, not primarily for measurement.
query_details: A protractor with degree markings (0–180°) used to measure angles; the image shows an angle being measured.

caption: A wheelbarrow in the grass.
distinguishing_feature: Wheelbarrow actively hauling bulk natural materials (soil/rocks/wood) in a typical working context, rather than being used decoratively, under repair, or as a non‑standard cart.
analysis: All group_a images show a standard single‑wheel wheelbarrow in active use hauling bulk natural materials (soil, gravel/snow, wood) or standing ready for such use. In group_b many examples are not in active hauling use: a repair scene, decorative planters with flowers, tipped display, or non‑standard/two‑wheel carts; only a minority show typical bulk‑material hauling.
query_details: A standard wheelbarrow filled with small rocks/gravel, appearing in a working outdoor setting.

caption: Foxes roaming on the prairie.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a red fox—reddish-orange coat, triangular ears, narrow muzzle, white throat, and a bushy tail (often pale-tipped).
analysis: All group_a images depict red foxes: small canids with reddish-orange fur, pointed ears, white throat/chest, and a bushy tail (often with a pale tip). Group_b images show other animals (raptor, snake, mouse, pronghorn, prairie dog, coyote) and not red foxes.
query_details: Multiple fox kits with reddish coats, pointed ears, and bushy tails standing on grass.

caption: A street corner in a suburban town.
distinguishing_feature: Low-rise, traditional main-street storefront architecture (quaint, historic facades with shops/awnings) indicative of a small-town/commercial district.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show small-town/main-street settings with 1–3 story historic or quaint storefronts, awnings, and walkable street corners. Group_b images depict large-scale urban scenes, aerials (farmland, suburbs), campuses, or dense city intersections with high-rises and heavy traffic—not small-town main streets.
query_details: Mountain resort village with low-rise, chalet-style buildings and a gondola; the buildings appear to be small-scale and storefront-like, set in a walkable setting—no high-rises or sprawling suburbia.

caption: Preschool kids.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of preschool/young children engaged in early-learning or play settings (vs. adults in group_b).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show young children in preschool/early classroom or play settings. Group_b images depict adults (young to elderly) engaged in classes, activities, or group exercises. The environments and participants' ages clearly differ.
query_details: A young child at a classroom chalkboard with numbers and shapes, indicative of an early-learning environment.

caption: A bunch of purple flowers.
distinguishing_feature: Dominance of purple/violet flowers (multiple blooms/arrangements) in the scene.
analysis: All group_a images prominently feature purple/violet flowers (fields, bouquets, arrangements, or clusters). Group_b images are not dominated by purple flowers—many are non-floral (balloons, grapes) or flowers of other colors; one has a single purple flower but not the recurring theme of abundant purple florals.
query_details: A bouquet composed mainly of purple flowers, labeled with purple flower types, centered in the image.

caption: A spoon full of food.
distinguishing_feature: A spoon/ladle visibly in use—holding, scooping, or pouring the food.
analysis: In group_a, every image includes a spoon or ladle actively holding/scooping/pouring food (sugar, seeds, pudding, soup). In group_b, utensils are either different (fork, spatula) or spoons are present but not in use/empty or off to the side.
query_details: Shows chia pudding with berries and a honey dipper drizzling honey; an empty wooden spoon lies nearby but is not holding food.

caption: Firefighters saving forest fires.
distinguishing_feature: Active suppression of an outdoor vegetation/wildland fire (flames in brush/forest with direct firefighting such as hose streams/drip torch/aerial drop).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show firefighters actively combating open-air vegetation/wildland fires—visible brush/forest flames, smoke, and suppression actions (hoses, drip torch, aerial water drop). Group_b images show firefighters in non-wildland or non-active suppression contexts (urban structure fire, rescue, posing/resting, staging) without clear open vegetation fire being fought.
query_details: Two firefighters in yellow wildland gear in a forest; one sprays water while the other digs the ground amid charred brush and smoke—typical wildland fire mop-up.

caption: Small animals that can fly.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a winged animal actively in flight (airborne with wings visible).
analysis: All group_a images show winged creatures captured in mid-air flight (butterflies, moths, ladybug taking off, dragonfly, bee, bats). Group_b images show animals that are not flying and generally lack wings (rodents, panda, fish, meerkat, otter, lizard).
query_details: Illustration of multiple butterflies flying above a flower field with wings open in the air.

caption: Firefighters saving forest fires.
distinguishing_feature: Active suppression of a wildfire in natural vegetation (forest/brush) outdoors.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show firefighters actively combating wildland/forest or brush fires in natural vegetation (trees/grass), often with hoses, drip torches, or aerial drops. Group_b shows firefighters in urban/structural contexts, portraits, rescues, or non-suppression scenes; when fire appears, it’s not a clear wildland suppression scene.
query_details: An illustration of firefighters using a hose to fight a forest fire among trees.

caption: Coins of various countries with human heads.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a prominent human head/bust portrait on the coin face.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show coins with clear human head/bust portraits on the visible side. Group_b images mostly show coins with maps, numbers, animals, symbols, or full-body figures, not portrait heads.
query_details: A pile of shiny gold coins each embossed with a side-view human head portrait.

caption: Baseball athletes on the field.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of baseball-specific context: bat/glove and players on a baseball diamond with bases and typical baseball uniforms/helmets.
analysis: Group_a images are all baseball/softball scenes on a diamond with bats, gloves, bases, and uniforms; group_b shows other sports (swimming, basketball, running/football field, golf).
query_details: A player in helmet and uniform swinging a bat on a baseball field with the diamond and stadium visible.

caption: An iron arch bridge.
distinguishing_feature: Visible metal truss/lattice arch structure forming the main span.
analysis: Group_a images all show bridges with exposed steel/iron truss or lattice arch structures (triangular/open frameworks). Group_b bridges are non‑truss: stone/wood arches, suspension footbridge, or solid deck structures without a visible lattice framework.
query_details: A large concrete viaduct with solid spans on piers; no exposed truss or lattice.

caption: A man riding a bicycle in the mountains.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a pedal bicycle being used or held by the person.
analysis: All group_a images show a person with a pedal bicycle (typically mountain biking outdoors). Group_b images depict other activities (hiking, mountaineering, skateboarding, horseback riding, motorcycling) with no bicycles present.
query_details: Silhouette of a person with a bicycle against a sunset sky.

caption: A white head seagull.
distinguishing_feature: Unhooded white head with gray back/wings (classic gull look) and a short, stout bill—no solid dark head hood.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show gulls with unhooded white heads and gray backs/wings, with a short, stout (often yellow) bill—typical coastal gull appearance. Group_b are other birds (toucan, eagles, pelicans, swan) plus one hooded gull with a dark head and red bill/legs.
query_details: A gull with a white unhooded head, gray wings/back, and yellow bill holding prey on wet sand.

caption: Steel beams of the building.
distinguishing_feature: Visible active construction (exposed structural skeleton, rebar, cranes/workers, unfinished surfaces) versus finished/installed structures.
analysis: Group_a images consistently depict active construction scenes with exposed frames/rebar, cranes, and workers—unfinished structures. Group_b images mostly show completed structures or non-construction objects, with little/no active building activity.
query_details: Completed glass curtain wall facade reflecting the sky; no exposed framing, equipment, or workers.

caption: American flag flying in the wind at the top of the flagpole.
distinguishing_feature: Flag flown at full-staff on a standard vertical flagpole (near the top of the pole).
analysis: Group_a consistently shows an American flag flying at the top of a standard vertical flagpole (full-staff), clean and elevated against the sky. Group_b images often show flags not at full-staff or not on a standard vertical pole (being raised, on a boat staff, tattered/on ground, or a different country’s flag), with only occasional full-staff cases.
query_details: An American flag is on a vertical pole positioned notably below the top—flying at half-staff.

caption: Red tiles on house roof.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of red/terracotta roof tiles across the roof surface.
analysis: All group_a images feature roofs with red/terracotta-colored tiles. Group_b images show roofs that are gray/green/black, asphalt shingles, or under construction without red tiles.
query_details: The roof has gray-brown tiles, not red/terracotta.

caption: A group of women wearing black dresses during a fashion show.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a fashion runway/catwalk setting with models actively presenting garments.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show fashion runway/catwalk presentations: models walking on a runway with show lighting/stage ambiance. Group_b mostly shows non-runway contexts (street, park, concert, casual group photo), with only one image resembling a runway finale.
query_details: A model in an elaborate gown walking in a show space, accompanied by another person—typical runway/finale scene.

caption: Dried curly leaves on the ground.
distinguishing_feature: Leaves/foliage as the primary subject (no prominent flowers) vs. images centered on flowers/petals or floral arrangements.
analysis: Group_a images are leaf-centric: fallen/dry leaves, leaf wreaths, foliage scenes—no prominent blossoms. Group_b images center on flowers/petals or floral arrangements (bouquets, blossoms), with one image of decorative branches rather than leaves. Thus, the consistent cue is leaves as the main subject vs flowers.
query_details: Close-up of green Monstera leaves with no flowers present.

caption: Flowers planted in the yard.
distinguishing_feature: A scene primarily filled with lush, colorful flowerbeds/lawns as the main subject (ornamental garden landscaping) versus scenes centered on functional structures/furniture or sparse/rocky/unfinished planting.
analysis: Group_a images are dominated by lush ornamental landscaping—broad lawns and dense, colorful flowerbeds or garden features (ponds/fountains). Group_b images show yards focused on human activities or utilitarian setups (play equipment, patio/table, greenhouse, gravel xeriscape, dead/bare beds) and lack expansive, blooming garden displays.
query_details: Patio seating area with sofas, table, rug, and a few potted plants by a pool—furniture and hardscape dominate; no expansive flowerbeds or lawn.

caption: Steel beams of the building.
distinguishing_feature: Active construction of steel/reinforced-concrete building frames (visible I-beams/rebar/cranes), as opposed to finished structures/objects or wood-only framing.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show active building construction scenes with exposed structural steel or reinforced-concrete elements (I-beams, rebar, cranes, workers). Group_b images are finished structures, standalone objects/materials, or wood-only framing without the heavy steel/rebar construction context.
query_details: Underside of a concrete slab with columns and scaffolding; marked grid lines on fresh concrete indicate an ongoing reinforced-concrete building construction site.

caption: English root word for forg.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of the exact letter sequence 'forg' in the visible text of the image.
analysis: Group_a images consistently contain visible text with the substring 'forg' (e.g., forgive, forgave, forgo, forging). Group_b images lack this specific 'forg' text, even when frogs appear.
query_details: The meme shows a childlike frog drawing labeled twice with the text 'forg'.

caption: Colorful ribbons.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of multiple brightly colored ribbons used as loose, flowing streamers/strips (often rainbow-like) as a central visual element.
analysis: Group_a consistently features ribbons as the main subject, shown in multiple bright colors and often as loose, flowing streamers or long tails. Group_b items mostly use ribbon in a more restrained/structured way (single-color bows, sewn-on stripes, wrapped fabric) rather than lots of free-flowing multicolored strands.
query_details: Collage of ribbon crafts showing many ribbons in various bright colors and patterns, with several loose strips and tails prominently displayed.

caption: A bouquet of flowers with oval petals.
distinguishing_feature: A single, prominently framed flower bloom with visible petals around a central disk (or a tidy arrangement of such blooms) as the primary subject, without animals or broad field scenes.
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature a clearly isolated flower bloom (or a neat bouquet/wreath of distinct blooms) as the main subject, with visible petals radiating from a center. Group_b images show fruits, leaves, an insect on a flower, or broad fields of flowers rather than a single, isolated blossom.
query_details: A simple line drawing of one daisy-like flower with petals radiating from a central disk—an isolated bloom.

caption: Opened shutters inside the room.
distinguishing_feature: Operable interior plantation shutters with adjustable louvers installed inside the window frame (light passes through angled slats).
analysis: Group_a consistently shows interior plantation shutters: adjustable horizontal louvers mounted within the window frame with light filtering through. Group_b images are mostly exterior/decorative shutters, solid board shutters, or roller shutters; when louvered, they are side panels or decor rather than operable interior window coverings.
query_details: Close-up of white interior plantation shutter panels with adjustable horizontal louvers and light filtering through.

caption: A fox playing in the snow.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a fox specifically in snow.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show a fox in a snowy environment. Group_b either shows snow without a fox or a fox in non-snowy settings (grass/forest).
query_details: A fox leaping in a grassy field with no snow visible.

caption: Tomato dishes.
distinguishing_feature: Clearly visible tomatoes or a red tomato-based sauce as a main visual component of the dish.
analysis: Group_a images all prominently feature tomatoes (fresh chunks/cherry tomatoes or a red tomato sauce). Group_b mostly lacks visible tomatoes, leaning toward creamy, egg, or green-based dishes; any tomato presence there is occasional and not dominant.
query_details: A pizza with a red tomato sauce base topped with vegetables and cheese.

caption: A pond surrounded by trees.
distinguishing_feature: An organic, natural water body with no visible constructed edging or container (natural shoreline in a larger landscape).
analysis: Group_a images show natural ponds/lakes in broader landscapes with irregular shorelines and dense vegetation; no hardscaping contains the water. Group_b images are decorative or artificial water features—small garden ponds with stone/concrete edging, containers, fountains, or stylized/illustrated scenes.
query_details: A painted natural scene with trees and a small waterfall feeding a pond; the shoreline is organic with no stone or built borders.

caption: A beautiful yard surrounding a country house.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a cultivated, private residential yard/patio directly associated with a home (lawn/garden/landscaping and domestic use).
analysis: Group_a images all depict private residential outdoor spaces—front/back yards or patios—often adjacent to a house and featuring lawn, garden beds, or patio/yard activities (seating, yard sale). Group_b images are non-residential scenes or objects: public parks/play areas, high‑rise building, courtyard, cemetery, landscape overlook, and a birdhouse—none are clearly a private home yard/patio.
query_details: Townhouse facade with porches and iron stairs, surrounded by landscaped shrubs/trees and a small front-yard garden and walkway—clearly a residential yard/patio area.

caption: Sharpened head screws.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of pointed, fully threaded wood/self‑tapping screws as the main subject.
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature wood/self‑tapping screws—pointed, fully threaded fasteners with driver heads. Group_b shows other objects or different fasteners (nails, blunt-ended bolts) and no pointed wood screws.
query_details: Metal mending plates accompanied by multiple pointed, threaded wood screws.

caption: Radio towers.
distinguishing_feature: Visible communication antennas (panel/dish) mounted on a mast or lattice tower.
analysis: Group_a images show telecommunications towers: tall masts or lattice structures with visible antenna hardware (panel arrays and/or microwave dishes). Group_b images are towers or stacks without communication antennas (sculptures, piles, lighthouse, watchtower).
query_details: Hilltop site with a red–white lattice mast bearing antenna panels/dishes next to a small equipment building.

caption: A girl with long curly hair.
distinguishing_feature: Long, loose, non-afro wavy/curly hair worn down past the shoulders.
analysis: All group_a images show long, loose, flowing wavy/curly hair worn down past the shoulders. Group_b images mostly feature short/tightly coiled afro-style curls, straight hair, or hair pulled back/with accessories, and generally not the long loose waves/curls seen in group_a.
query_details: Subject has long, loose, flowing wavy/curly hair worn down past the shoulders.

caption: A rat in a trap.
distinguishing_feature: A rodent actively interacting with a trap (caught or on the trap).
analysis: All group_a images show a rodent physically on/in a mousetrap or glue trap (often caught). Group_b images show rodents without traps, or traps without a real rodent, or unrelated subjects.
query_details: A rat on wooden boards with no trap visible or interaction with any trap.

caption: A lighthouse by the sea.
distinguishing_feature: A clearly visible lighthouse is present.
analysis: All group_a images prominently feature a lighthouse in a coastal setting. Group_b images are mixed maritime/nautical scenes or other subjects; only a couple include a lighthouse, so the presence of a lighthouse is not consistent in group_b.
query_details: A miniature coastal diorama with a striped lighthouse by the water.

caption: Cartoon unicorn.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of an equine (horse-like) figure with a single forehead horn (unicorn).
analysis: All group_a images depict a unicorn—an equine with a single horn on its forehead—while group_b shows various non‑equine animals (owl, dog, bear, elephant, cat, dragon) without a single unicorn horn.
query_details: Shows a white horse-like creature with a single horn on its forehead in a fantasy forest.

caption: Multi layer cake.
distinguishing_feature: A stacked, frosted layer cake (two or more layers) presented as a finished decorated cake.
analysis: Group_a images are all finished, decorated layer cakes—stacked with frosting between layers or fully iced with toppings (fruit, drip, flowers). Group_b images show undecorated or single-layer bases, other pastry forms (pie crust, cupcakes), or simple loaf slices—no stacked, frosted celebration cakes.
query_details: A tall frosted cake decorated with colorful flowers on top, indicating a finished layered celebration cake.

caption: A stack of money.
distinguishing_feature: A human hand directly holding the money (present in group_b; absent in group_a).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show money lying on surfaces or in stacks/bundles with no hand directly holding it. Group_b frequently shows a person/hand actively holding or manipulating money (or money in containers like a piggy bank/jar).
query_details: A suited hand is gripping a wad of U.S. dollar bills.

caption: A colorful rainbow over the grassland.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a natural rainbow arch in the sky (not colors on man‑made objects or abstract art).
analysis: All group_a images depict a natural atmospheric rainbow arc spanning the sky over landscapes (often double). Group_b images show rainbow colors on objects/food/art or scenes without a sky rainbow.
query_details: Shows a rainbow-colored umbrella on a beach; no atmospheric rainbow arc in the sky.

caption: Horses on the grassland.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a horse as a primary subject in the scene.
analysis: All group_a images prominently feature at least one horse (often being ridden or in a pasture). In group_b most images have no horse; only a couple include a horse, so the presence of a horse is not consistent there.
query_details: Two people outdoors with a saddled horse being led through a mountainous landscape; the horse is clearly a main subject.

caption: A bridge across a river.
distinguishing_feature: A bridge is the primary subject and it clearly crosses over visible water beneath the span.
analysis: All group_a images prominently feature a bridge spanning over a visible body of water, with the water clearly seen under the bridge. Group_b images are mostly not bridges or are bridges not clearly over water (gorge/forest), or the bridge is not the main subject (e.g., castle scene, fountains, golf course).
query_details: An aerial view of a cable-stayed road bridge with cars, clearly spanning over a large body of water.

caption: Christmas illustration.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of clear, traditional Christmas iconography and celebrations (e.g., Santa, nativity, decorated tree with ornaments/gifts, stockings, caroling, gingerbread) in a conventional festive context.
analysis: Group_a consistently shows classic, traditional Christmas motifs (Santa and reindeer, decorated tree with ornaments and gifts, stockings by a fireplace, carolers, gingerbread) in conventional festive settings. Group_b images either depict generic winter scenes or Christmas elements placed in unconventional/out-of-place contexts (beach/desert scenes, mashups, undecorated tree).
query_details: A nativity scene with figures around a manger under a starry night—an iconic, traditional Christmas depiction.

caption: Colored pencils.
distinguishing_feature: Visible multicolored, wood‑cased colored pencils with sharpened tips present in the scene.
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature wood‑cased colored pencils (often multiple colors) either being used or displayed, sometimes alongside artwork made with them. Group_b images show other stationery or drawing media (mechanical pencil lead, graphite pencil with eraser, woodless color sticks, sharpeners, notebook) and only occasionally artwork without the pencils present.
query_details: Shows several sharpened colored pencils arranged above a rainbow drawing with the word 'Rainbow'.

caption: A field of red poppies.
distinguishing_feature: A natural outdoor poppy field scene with many red poppies filling the frame (landscape context with horizon/sky).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show outdoor landscape scenes dominated by dense fields of red poppies, often with horizon/sky visible. Group_b images lack this: they show isolated flowers on white, a single poppy in a vase, people in grass, non-poppy flower beds, or illustrations.
query_details: A bouquet of red poppy stems isolated on a white background, not a field or landscape.

caption: A cross sea bridge.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a long bridge/viaduct crossing open sea water (often with multiple piers or cable-stayed sections).
analysis: Group_a images consistently show long bridges or causeways spanning over the sea/ocean. Group_b images depict ocean/coastal scenes, objects, or non-sea bridges/tunnels, but not long sea-spanning bridges.
query_details: A seabird flying over ocean waves; no bridge or man-made sea-spanning structure visible.

caption: Extremely tall skyscrapers.
distinguishing_feature: A prominently featured, extremely tall and slender tower/skyscraper that stands much higher than nearby structures and is the main subject of the image.
analysis: Group_a images consistently highlight a single ultra-tall, very slender skyscraper/tower dominating the scene, usually centered and towering above its surroundings. Group_b images depict vehicles, nature, or general skylines without one dominant skinny tower.
query_details: A park scene with a very thin supertall skyscraper prominently rising above the skyline, clearly the dominant vertical element.

caption: Opened shutters inside the room.
distinguishing_feature: Interior plantation shutters with adjustable louvers and a visible tilt bar within framed panels on the window/door.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show interior plantation shutters: framed panels with thick horizontal louvers and visible tilt bars covering actual windows/doors inside living spaces. Group_b images are exterior shutters, solid/rolling panels, or decorative/fixed-louver pieces without the interior framed, tilt‑bar look.
query_details: Boat windows with thin horizontal blinds behind the glass; no framed shutter panels or central tilt bar.

caption: A symbol of king.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a crown as the main visual element.
analysis: All group_a images prominently feature a crown (royal headpiece). Group_b images show other medieval/fantasy symbols (castle, horse, jester, dragon, shield) but no crowns.
query_details: Two stylized crowns, one black and one gold, centered on a white background.

caption: A herd of cattle grazing on a pasture.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of clearly visible black-and-white piebald body pattern (Holstein-type) on the cows.
analysis: All group_a images include cows with clear black-and-white piebald (Holstein-like) body patterns, often grazing in open pasture. Group_b mostly shows solid-colored (black or brown) cattle or other contexts, with black-and-white piebald bodies largely absent or rare.
query_details: Cattle are mostly solid black with white faces; no large black-and-white piebald body patches are visible.

caption: A walking reindeer.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of prominent branched antlers on the animal’s head.
analysis: All group_a images show deer/reindeer with clearly visible branched antlers. In group_b, most subjects either lack antlers (does/fawns) or are not deer; a few may show antlers but inconsistently.
query_details: A spotted deer grazing on grass with no antlers visible.

caption: Decorated with fake feathers.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of feathers/plumage (visible quills, barbs, or feather-shaped decorative pieces).
analysis: All group_a images feature feathers or items decorated with feathers, while group_b images depict unrelated subjects (people, plants, wood, machinery, bricks, flowers) with no feathers.
query_details: A teardrop pendant covered with crystals/gemstones; metallic jewelry with no feathers present.

caption: Red bows.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a red bow/bow tie.
analysis: All group_a images feature a red bow or bow tie. Group_b shows bows/bow ties of other colors and patterns (blue, green, purple, multicolor), with red appearing only occasionally and not as the consistent theme.
query_details: A woman wearing a red dress with a prominent red bow at the chest.

caption: Instruments for quantitative measurements.
distinguishing_feature: Designed primarily to measure/quantify with a scale, markings, or readout (measurement instruments) vs. tools for manipulating materials with no measurement scale.
analysis: Group_a images are all measuring instruments (thermometer, multimeter, caliper, barometer, bathroom scale, measuring tape) showing scales, numbers, or displays. Group_b images are general hand/power tools used to act on materials (stapler/clip, saw, brush, drill, screwdriver, hammer).
query_details: A combination/ratcheting wrench used to tighten or loosen nuts and bolts; no measurement markings or readout.

caption: A herd of cattle grazing on a pasture.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of black-and-white piebald (Holstein-style) cows.
analysis: Group_a images consistently feature black-and-white piebald dairy cows (Holstein-like) visible in open pastures. Group_b images mostly show solid-colored brown/black cattle or brown-white patterns, often near fences/barns or in non-pasture contexts; notably, they lack the classic black-and-white Holstein pattern.
query_details: Shows brown/reddish cows behind an electric fence near a barn; no black-and-white Holstein pattern visible.

caption: The girl has long and thin braids on her head.
distinguishing_feature: Multiple small, tight braids/cornrows anchored to the scalp (protective style) vs. loose single braids or accessory-based hairstyles.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show protective braided styles: many small, tight plaits or cornrows anchored to the scalp (box braids, feed-in/cornrow patterns, microbraids). Group_b shows either a single loose braid, decorative accessories, or non-scalp-anchored styles; no dense rows of scalp cornrows/box braids.
query_details: Hair is arranged in neat parallel cornrows feeding into long braids—tight, scalp-anchored protective style.

caption: Handwritten notes on the blackboard.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of genuine handwritten chalk writing/drawings on a chalkboard surface (with chalk strokes/smudges), not printed/digital graphics or blank boards.
analysis: All group_a images show real chalkboards covered with handwritten chalk text/diagrams. Group_b images are either clean/blank boards, printed or digital graphics, or setups without actual chalk handwriting (occasionally a small chalk mark but not a board full of handwriting).
query_details: A child is drawing a figure with white chalk on a green chalkboard; clear chalk lines and smudges are visible.

caption: A town surrounded by mountains.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of a dense settlement (multiple buildings/streets) integrated into a mountainous landscape.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show mountain towns—clusters of buildings and streets nestled in valleys or along mountain slopes. Group_b shows mountains without a town: wilderness scenes, a lone house, individual activity, or isolated/futuristic structures.
query_details: Mountain range with haze; mid-ground shows a spread of buildings forming a town across the valley/slopes.

caption: Mushrooms on the green meadow.
distinguishing_feature: Presence of real mushrooms/fungal fruiting bodies or clear fungal growth phenomena.
analysis: Group_a consistently shows real mushrooms/fungal growth (fruiting bodies) often in grass or natural settings. Group_b shows rural scenes, animals, flowers, or a man‑made mushroom-shaped object, but no actual fungi growing.
query_details: Three lawn photos showing fairy rings, including a visible ring of mushrooms and fungal rings in grass.

caption: Motorcycles parked on the empty street.
distinguishing_feature: A lineup of several parked motorcycles/scooters close together along a curb or designated parking area.
analysis: Group_a images consistently show multiple motorcycles or scooters parked closely together in a line along a curb or parking area. Group_b images typically feature a single motorcycle (or widely separated bikes) and not a clustered lineup, sometimes with a rider or in open/isolated settings.
query_details: Several motorcycles/scooters are parked side by side in a row in front of shops, with a parking sign visible.

caption: A wooden pier by the calm river.
distinguishing_feature: A pier/dock/jetty projecting over the water from the shore.
analysis: All group_a images feature a wooden pier/dock/jetty extending from shore out over the water. Group_b images show water scenes without such a dock (boats, shoreline, bridge, bench, cabin).
query_details: An aerial view shows a long wooden dock with a small hut extending into turquoise water from the shore.

caption: Military helicopters are carrying out rescues.
